expression.expression:
CASE 
    WHEN LOWER(TRIM(SHTRDJ)) = 'null' OR TRIM(SHTRDJ) = '' OR TRIM(SHTRDJ) = '0' THEN NULL 
    ELSE to_timestamp(
                        substr(CAST(date_add(
                                            concat(substr(CAST(CAST(TRIM(SHTRDJ)
 AS INT) + 1900000 AS STRING),1,4),'-01-01'), 
 CAST(substr(CAST(CAST(TRIM(SHTRDJ) AS INT) + 1900000 AS string),5,4) AS INT )-1) AS STRING), 1, 10),'yyyy-MM-dd') END
